---
import CTAButton from './CTAButton.astro';
---

<section class="py-20">
  <div class="container-main">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl rounded-2xl border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30 p-8 sm:p-12">
      <div class="mb-6 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-emerald-500/10 text-2xl">
        🔐
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-100 sm:text-3xl">The ZDR Pledge</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-emerald-400 font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase">Zero Data Retention</p>

      <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-slate-300">
        <p>
          <strong class="text-slate-100">ZDR (Zero Data Retention)</strong> means exactly that.
        </p>
        <p>
          Your conversation history lives in your browser's IndexedDB.
          Your API key is stored locally.
          We run no servers, maintain no databases, log nothing.
        </p>
        <p>
          Configure privacy enforcement at the OpenRouter account level,
          and every request is ZDR-guaranteed at the network layer.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-6 rounded-lg bg-slate-900/50 p-4 text-sm text-slate-400">
        <p>
          <strong class="text-slate-200">We have no financial stake.</strong>
          We're not affiliated with OpenRouter.ai. We don't earn commissions, resell tokens,
          or track your usage. The app costs us ~$0/month to host on Cloudflare's free tier.
          We built this because private AI should be accessible — not for profit.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8">
        <CTAButton href="/docs/privacy-and-security" variant="secondary">Learn About Our Privacy Model</CTAButton>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>